REGULATORY SOURCE MATERIAL
--------------------------
The Software incorporates summaries of, references to, and direct quotations
from regulations issued by the State Bank of Pakistan (SBP), the Securities
and Exchange Commission of Pakistan (SECP), the Financial Monitoring Unit
(FMU), the National Database and Registration Authority (NADRA), the
Pakistan Telecommunication Authority (PTA), the Ministry of Information
Technology and Telecommunication (MoITT), the Ministry of Finance (MoF),
and the Pakistan Banks Association (PBA), and from primary legislation of
the Islamic Republic of Pakistan.

These underlying regulatory documents remain the property of, and are
subject to use restrictions imposed by, their respective issuers. The
verbatim quotes and source-URL references in this Software are included
under fair-use principles for compliance and educational purposes. Nothing
in this licence grants any right in the underlying regulatory documents
themselves; consult the issuing regulator's official portal for the
authoritative text.

